<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 18:09:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“内塔尼亚胡可以被驱逐吗？以色列如何决定暗杀谁？以及《国土报》读者提出的其他紧迫问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-01-17/ty-article-podcast/can-netanyahu-be-ousted-and-other-burning-questions-from-haaretz-readers/0000018d-174b-d7c2-a1cd-37cfd5030000</link><description>我们邀请订阅者向《国土报》记者和分析人士提出有关加沙战争的问题。在本周的《国土报》播客中，您可以听到他们的答案</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 17:33:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-01-17/ty-article-podcast/can-netanyahu-be-ousted-and-other-burning-questions-from-haaretz-readers/0000018d-174b-d7c2-a1cd-37cfd5030000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军表示不清楚加沙三名人质是如何死亡的，但他们可能是中毒或窒息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/idf-says-not-clear-how-three-hostages-died-but-they-may-have-been-poisoned-or-suffocated/0000018d-17f5-dd75-addd-f7f5e2e10000</link><description>以色列军队于 12 月遣返了在加沙被杀的三名人质（一名平民和两名士兵）的尸体，有关他们死亡情况的问题仍然悬而未决</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 16:54:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/idf-says-not-clear-how-three-hostages-died-but-they-may-have-been-poisoned-or-suffocated/0000018d-17f5-dd75-addd-f7f5e2e10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列左翼 MK 因袭击警察情节严重而被起诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-left-wing-mk-indicted-for-assaulting-police-officer-under-aggravated-circumstances/0000018d-17c2-d695-a3dd-57e7a68b0000</link><description>2022 年，MK 奥弗·卡西夫 (MK Ofer Cassif) 在前往约旦河西岸马萨费尔·亚塔 (Masafer Yatta) 地区举行示威活动时，被拍到击中一名警察的头部，抗议最高法院下令驱逐巴勒斯坦家庭的裁决。卡西夫称起诉书是政治迫害</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 15:39:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-left-wing-mk-indicted-for-assaulting-police-officer-under-aggravated-circumstances/0000018d-17c2-d695-a3dd-57e7a68b0000</guid></item><item><title>大屠杀纪念馆主席回应50名大屠杀研究人员的来信：大多数以色列人反对种族灭绝的呼吁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/yad-vashem-chairman-rejects-request-to-condemn-calls-for-genocide-in-gaza/0000018d-17a7-d695-a3dd-57a778100000</link><description>达尼·达扬 (Dani Dayan) 在回复 50 位大屠杀学者的来信时表示，这些学者未能解决问题的大背景，而且大多数以色列人和以色列军队不支持此类呼吁</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 15:29:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/yad-vashem-chairman-rejects-request-to-condemn-calls-for-genocide-in-gaza/0000018d-17a7-d695-a3dd-57a778100000</guid></item><item><title>以色列司法部表示，必须缓和以色列当局监督阿拉伯教师的法案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/justice-ministry-calls-to-tone-down-bill-giving-authorities-oversight-of-arab-teachers/0000018d-17c2-d1f2-a79f-97ffca700000</link><description>“对某人的思想施加严厉的行政处罚并不是一件简单的事情” ■ 司法部官员试图限制以色列当局解雇教师的权力；极右翼赞助商反对任何改变</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 15:24:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/justice-ministry-calls-to-tone-down-bill-giving-authorities-oversight-of-arab-teachers/0000018d-17c2-d1f2-a79f-97ffca700000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日之后你如何保持人文主义？这位以色列剧作家试图找出答案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-01-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-to-remain-humanistic-after-a-massacre-this-israeli-playwright-tries-to-find-out/0000018d-17be-d695-a3dd-57bf0c370000</link><description>10 月 7 日后几天，玛雅·阿拉德·亚苏尔 (Maya Arad Yasur) 撰写了《如何在 17 步大屠杀后保持人道主义》，并在雅法剧院上演。她说：“我认为目前人文主义者很难继续保持人文主义者的身份”</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 14:43:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-01-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-to-remain-humanistic-after-a-massacre-this-israeli-playwright-tries-to-find-out/0000018d-17be-d695-a3dd-57bf0c370000</guid></item><item><title>周二，两名以色列国防军预备役士兵在加沙地带北部的战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/two-idf-reservist-soldeirs-killed-on-tuesday-in-north-gaza-strip-fighting/0000018d-175c-d1f2-a79f-977d21af0000</link><description>这两名士兵被任命为军士长。 （res.）撒迦利亚·佩萨赫·哈伯（Zechariah Pesach Haber）和中士。 Yair Katz 少校；以色列国防军报告称，过去一天有 17 名士兵在加沙地带的战斗中受伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 13:40:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/two-idf-reservist-soldeirs-killed-on-tuesday-in-north-gaza-strip-fighting/0000018d-175c-d1f2-a79f-977d21af0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列考古学家在耶路撒冷附近发现了一半非常早期的硬币</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-01-17/ty-article/israeli-archaeologists-find-half-of-very-early-coin-near-jerusalem/0000018d-174a-d7c2-a1cd-37ce9be60000</link><description>这枚 2,550 年前的硬币是在耶路撒冷第一圣殿时代的住宅中发现的，它已被一分为二，表明它已降级为按重量白银支付的前货币状态</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 13:01:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-01-17/ty-article/israeli-archaeologists-find-half-of-very-early-coin-near-jerusalem/0000018d-174a-d7c2-a1cd-37ce9be60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队征召并武装了数千名定居者。关于他们的暴力行为的记录正在堆积如山</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-army-drafted-thousands-of-settlers-accounts-of-their-violence-are-piling-up/0000018d-12e7-d260-aded-b7efddbe0000</link><description>自加沙战争爆发以来，“区域防御”营已增加五倍，越来越多的报道称，在其中服役的定居者袭击和威胁巴勒斯坦人</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 12:34:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-army-drafted-thousands-of-settlers-accounts-of-their-violence-are-piling-up/0000018d-12e7-d260-aded-b7efddbe0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡联盟提出扩大警察权力以限制嫌疑人行动的法案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-coalition-advances-bill-expanding-police-powers-to-restrict-suspects-movements/0000018d-170f-d1f2-a79f-977f31d60000</link><description>除其他外，该立法将允许软禁最多 15 天，而目前的软禁时间为 5 天。尽管司法部长反对且紧急政府同意禁止非战争相关立法，但该法案仍在继续推进</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 12:12:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-coalition-advances-bill-expanding-police-powers-to-restrict-suspects-movements/0000018d-170f-d1f2-a79f-977f31d60000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯称以色列不会检查加沙人质运送的药品；内塔尼亚胡：“军队有责任”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/medicine-for-hostages-arrive-in-egypt-top-hamas-official-israel-wont-inspect-shipment/0000018d-170e-d1f2-a79f-977fdd720000</link><description>哈马斯的阿布·马尔祖克还表示，该协议允许“为人质提供一箱毒品，以换取巴勒斯坦人民的 1,000 箱毒品”。以色列不是该协议的积极参与方，但同意卡塔尔可以自行安排药品和人道主义援助进入加沙</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 11:17:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/medicine-for-hostages-arrive-in-egypt-top-hamas-official-israel-wont-inspect-shipment/0000018d-170e-d1f2-a79f-977fdd720000</guid></item><item><title>国家撤销对 18 岁以色列人的案件，该男子在司法改革抗议期间被警察殴打</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/state-drops-case-against-18-year-old-israeli-pictured-punched-by-police-officer/0000018d-16dd-d695-a3dd-56fda73e0000</link><description>州检方决定撤销此案，但没有对这一决定做出任何解释。去年夏天警察部长本-格维尔赞扬了这名警官的行为后，警方对该警官的内部调查已经完成，现在正在等待检察官的决定</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 10:43:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/state-drops-case-against-18-year-old-israeli-pictured-punched-by-police-officer/0000018d-16dd-d695-a3dd-56fda73e0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列的政治和军事领导人想要一场永久的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/why-israels-political-and-military-leaders-want-a-perpetual-war/0000018d-125e-dac4-a9cf-527fb7820000</link><description>该国许多决策者似乎对以色列与哈马斯的战争持续下去且看不到结束的局面感到着迷。这就是为什么它可以使他们受益</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 09:28:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/why-israels-political-and-military-leaders-want-a-perpetual-war/0000018d-125e-dac4-a9cf-527fb7820000</guid></item><item><title>由于内塔尼亚胡的政治算计，以色列与哈马斯的人质协议退居二线</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/hamas-or-hostages-israeli-army-agonizes-over-two-conflicting-goals-in-gaza/0000018d-13e2-dd15-a7af-9fef130b0000</link><description>尽管有美国的压力，内塔尼亚胡唯一担心的“后一天”是拜登之后的事。 ■ 战时内阁因人质释放而陷入分裂，对内塔尼亚胡来说，他的联盟是第一位的。如果甘茨和艾森科特退出紧急政府，可能会在以色列街头引发大规模抗议浪潮</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 04:03:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/hamas-or-hostages-israeli-army-agonizes-over-two-conflicting-goals-in-gaza/0000018d-13e2-dd15-a7af-9fef130b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队公布了两名阵亡士兵的名字；运送给以色列人质的药品</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article-live/kibbutz-beeri-announces-the-deaths-of-israeli-hostages-itay-svirsky-and-yossi-sharabi/0000018d-156d-d260-aded-b7edc14d0000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，他们在隔夜空袭中消灭了计划“迫在眉睫的袭击”的约旦河西岸恐怖组织，巴勒斯坦人报告称，以色列国防军在图尔卡尔姆的空袭中有四人死亡。人质抵达埃及，哈马斯称以色列不会检查他们 ■ 周二，两名以色列国防军预备役人员在加沙战斗中丧生</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 03:26:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article-live/kibbutz-beeri-announces-the-deaths-of-israeli-hostages-itay-svirsky-and-yossi-sharabi/0000018d-156d-d260-aded-b7edc14d0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔部继续发放枪支许可证，以色列却在心理健康检查上磨蹭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-dawdles-on-mental-health-checks-as-ministry-continues-to-dole-out-gun-permits/0000018d-141e-dd15-a7af-9e7ff8620000</link><description>国家安全部尚未对申请携带武器许可证的以色列人实施扩大且更严格的卫生部调查问卷；本-格维尔的部门表示，调查问卷需要“更加精确”</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 23:38:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-dawdles-on-mental-health-checks-as-ministry-continues-to-dole-out-gun-permits/0000018d-141e-dd15-a7af-9e7ff8620000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔证实：为以色列人质提供的药品将于周三进入加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/qatar-confirms-medicine-for-israeli-hostages-will-enter-gaza-on-wednesday/0000018d-141e-d260-aded-b7be3dd40000</link><description>多哈斡旋协议的细节仍不明确，但以色列已同意大幅增加进入加沙的药品数量</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 21:25:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/qatar-confirms-medicine-for-israeli-hostages-will-enter-gaza-on-wednesday/0000018d-141e-d260-aded-b7be3dd40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列教育部长不停地从一个血腥恐怖场景跳到另一个场景</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-education-minister-keeps-dancing-from-one-bloody-terror-scene-to-another/0000018d-13e3-d727-a3cf-73e37f700000</link><description>周二，我们看到了另一令人作呕的景象，就在一天前，教育部长 Yoav Kisch 在一次恐怖袭击现场加入了一群十几岁男孩的喧闹舞蹈，其中一名妇女被谋杀，另外 17 人受伤，其中许多人伤势严重。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 21:08:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-education-minister-keeps-dancing-from-one-bloody-terror-scene-to-another/0000018d-13e3-d727-a3cf-73e37f700000</guid></item><item><title>世界认真解决巴以冲突吗？我们最好希望如此</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/is-the-world-serious-about-solving-the-israel-palestine-conflict-wed-better-hope-so/0000018d-1345-d260-aded-b7ed9aa70000</link><description>“我们不会回到 10 月 6 日”是目前驻中东的外国使节的常见说法。但是，这是什么意思？世界对该地区的战后未来有何设想？两国解决方案如何融入其中？</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 20:32:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/is-the-world-serious-about-solving-the-israel-palestine-conflict-wed-better-hope-so/0000018d-1345-d260-aded-b7ed9aa70000</guid></item><item><title>贝埃里基布兹宣布以色列人质伊泰·斯维尔斯基和尤西·沙拉比死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/israeli-hostages-itay-svirsky-and-yossi-sharabi-killed-during-captivity-in-gaza/0000018d-13ce-d727-a3cf-73efc2360000</link><description>贝埃里基布兹宣布这一消息之前，哈马斯周日发布了一段视频，视频中显示两人与另一名以色列人质诺亚·阿加马尼 (Noa Argamani) 在一起</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 20:25:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/israeli-hostages-itay-svirsky-and-yossi-sharabi-killed-during-captivity-in-gaza/0000018d-13ce-d727-a3cf-73efc2360000</guid></item></channel></rss>